# Matrix Project Path Registry
# Maps filesystem paths to canonical project names.
# Used to identify which project a session is working on,
# even when the session started in ~ and edits files elsewhere.
#
# Format: path|project-name
# Paths are prefix-matched (more specific paths take priority)
#
# DO NOT add paths that appear in every session's scrollback
# (e.g. ~/.claude/hooks) — those would make every session
# look like the same project.
#
# Examples:
#   ~/Projects/my-app/src|my-app
#   ~/Desktop/my-tool|my-tool
